content: I have gathered a good number of contacts with their answers. How is that delivered to you?
You can fill out the Survey tab in the [Person screen](https://www.reach.vote/knowledge-base/person-profile-screen/)
Thanks, but how is this sent in to be useful?
When you click on "save", the answers will be available to the campaign.  If I'm not understanding your question, try asking in https://events.democrats.org/event/597621/
